{"id":35732,"date":"2024-02-03T09:30:00","date_gmt":"2024-02-03T04:00:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=35732"},"modified":"2023-03-31T15:38:37","modified_gmt":"2023-03-31T10:08:37","slug":"curved-sofa-designs","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/curved-sofa-designs\/","title":{"rendered":"7 Curved Sofa Designs That Will Make Heads Turn"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Ditch the ordinary for your living room and opt for a unique curved sofa design instead.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>It is not often that we see the drastic change that happens to furniture. We are talking sofas here \u2014 one of the significant elements of every living room. Curved sofa, in particular. Its root goes way back to the \u201970s when furniture designers began experimenting with silhouettes and adopted more feminine features.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Curved sofas are definite conversation starters. Pushing aside streamlined straight and sharp edges, curves are making a comeback in furniture silhouettes after almost 40 years. Swap your old conventional couch with one of these curved sofa designs and witness how your guests gravitate towards it. Here\u2019s how you can dip your toes into this furniture trend without breaking your bank.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Curved Sofa Set Can Bring Softness To Your Living Room Decor<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Take a break from standard <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/mid-century-modern-interior-design-ideas\/\">mid-century style<\/a> furniture and add a dash of softness with this curved sofa. It has a charming way of softening the look of your home effortlessly. The white traditional curved sofa instantly stands out in this colourful room. We have channelled a traditional Indian look with vibrant wallpaper, heritage paintings, bronze pendant lights, beaded room partition and intricately-curved marble coffee table with brass table decor.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02105445\/white-traditional-curved-sofa.jpg\" alt=\"White traditional curved sofa stands out in colourful room\" class=\"wp-image-35739\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02105445\/white-traditional-curved-sofa.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02105445\/white-traditional-curved-sofa-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02105445\/white-traditional-curved-sofa-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02105445\/white-traditional-curved-sofa-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Enhance the room\u2019s allure with a curved sofa design<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Introduce Timeless Charm To Your Small Living Room With A Curved Sofa<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Curved sofas are a great solution for small apartments. You can make a big impact on a small budget. They work wonders for snug spaces. A pastel green curved sectional sofa adds character to the all-white decor of this living room and elevates its style quotient. We have also placed a tufted wing back chair in powder blue for that extra oomph.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02105425\/pastel-green-curved-sectional-sofa.jpg\" alt=\"Pastel green curved sectional sofa makes a big impact on a small budget\" class=\"wp-image-35736\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02105425\/pastel-green-curved-sectional-sofa.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02105425\/pastel-green-curved-sectional-sofa-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02105425\/pastel-green-curved-sectional-sofa-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02105425\/pastel-green-curved-sectional-sofa-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A curved sectional sofa is classic and comfortable<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"End-to-end home interior design solutions for a stunning home\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180939\/end-to-end-home-interior-design-solutions-for-stunning-home.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Make A Statement With A Curved Double-Sided Sofa<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have ample space in your living room, don\u2019t let the lack of seating stop you from having a meaningful conversation. This plush purple <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/double-sided-sofa\/\">double-sided sofa<\/a> is the focal point of this grey living room and a total conversation starter. The sofa\u2019s abstract shape creates multiple nooks for cosy seating. Now you can enjoy reading your favourite book while enjoying the company of your family watching a movie on the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/wall-mounted-tv-cabinet-designs\/\">wall-mounted TV<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02105412\/curved-double-sided-sofa-in-plush-purple.jpg\" alt=\"Curved double sided sofa in plush purple creates multiple nooks for cosy seating\" class=\"wp-image-35734\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02105412\/curved-double-sided-sofa-in-plush-purple.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02105412\/curved-double-sided-sofa-in-plush-purple-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02105412\/curved-double-sided-sofa-in-plush-purple-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02105412\/curved-double-sided-sofa-in-plush-purple-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A curved contemporary sofa for extra seating<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Curved Sofa Design For The Balcony To Relish Breezy Evenings<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Bring in this lime yellow and striped art deco-style small curved leather sofa if you want to give your balcony an effortless, whimsical vibe. The multipurpose soft yellow bar cabinet with extra seating is perfect for hosting a small get-together with friends and family. You can use a fake grass patch rug and a small metal coffee table to add definition to your balcony.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02105438\/small-curved-sofa-in-lime-yellow-for-balcony.jpg\" alt=\"Small curved sofa in lime yellow for balcony\" class=\"wp-image-35738\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02105438\/small-curved-sofa-in-lime-yellow-for-balcony.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02105438\/small-curved-sofa-in-lime-yellow-for-balcony-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02105438\/small-curved-sofa-in-lime-yellow-for-balcony-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02105438\/small-curved-sofa-in-lime-yellow-for-balcony-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Enjoy some cocktails on this \u200barmless curved sofa<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Add An Edge To Your Living Room With A Curved Leather Sofa<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Enjoy a glass of bourbon in your den or a bag of popcorn while watching a movie with your family on this 5-seater curved sofa. It suits any decor despite its bold vibe. The blue curved leather sofa is the centre of attraction in this white and grey living room. We have paired the couch with a classic white wingback accent chair. The ultra-wide couch created the perfect setting for a massive gallery wall.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02105406\/blue-curved-leather-sofa.jpg\" alt=\"Curved leather sofa suits any decor despite its bold vibe\" class=\"wp-image-35733\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02105406\/blue-curved-leather-sofa.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02105406\/blue-curved-leather-sofa-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02105406\/blue-curved-leather-sofa-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02105406\/blue-curved-leather-sofa-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Up your style game with a curved leather sofa<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"https:\/\/api.whatsapp.com\/send?phone=916366910437&text=Hello%20Design%20Cafe%20Team,%20I%20am%20interested%20to%20know%20more%20about%20your%20home%20interior%20design%20services\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Do you want a dream home with interiors that last a lifetime\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/26185038\/dream-home-with-interiors-that-last-a-lifetime.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Semicircle Curved Sofa Is A Functional Work Of Art<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Curvy sofas are excellent functioning pieces of art. They are great investment choices, unlike your regular ol\u2019 couches. This semicircle mauve-coloured velvet sofa is the best place for thoughtful conversations and intimate gatherings. So, if you like to host and entertain often, this kind of sofa is an excellent choice for you.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02105431\/semi-circle-curved-modular-sofa.jpg\" alt=\"Semi-circle curved modular sofa is excellent functioning pieces of art\" class=\"wp-image-35737\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02105431\/semi-circle-curved-modular-sofa.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02105431\/semi-circle-curved-modular-sofa-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02105431\/semi-circle-curved-modular-sofa-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/02105431\/semi-circle-curved-modular-sofa-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A semicircle curved sofa for a unique look<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Did this blog inspire you to join the evergreen trend of curved sofas? If you need help with custom designing your dream piece, our designers are here for you. Book an appointment today and they will guide you through every detail. We are specialists in uber-cool homes. Check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/\">our blog<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/guides\/\">guides section<\/a> to know more about the latest home interior trends.<\/p>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Lookin